<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
  <title>Welcome!</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="img/favicon-32x32.png">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC" crossorigin="anonymous">  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/f5c7d6a886.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/aos@next/dist/aos.css">
  <link href="css/starter.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
</head>

<body>

<header>
  <h1 data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-duration="700" data-aos-delay="200" id="name">FlickFusion</h1>
  <h3 data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-delay="1000" class="text-center text-white mt-3" id="underName">Online Video Hosting</h3>
</header>

<section>
  <div class="image-container">
    <img
      src="img/onlineCinema.jpg"
      alt="Online Movies"
      data-aos="fade-up"
      data-aos-duration="1000"
      data-aos-offset="250"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="description">
    <h2 data-aos="fade-zoom-in" data-aos-duration="1000" data-aos-offset="250">Online Movies & Series</h2>
    <p data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-duration="1000" data-aos-delay="100" data-aos-offset="250">
      Welcome to our world of endless entertainment! Dive into a universe filled with captivating
      movies and series, available at your fingertips. Stream hassle-free, anytime, anywhere, and embark on
      thrilling adventures with our vast library of content. From the latest blockbusters to timeless
      classics, elevate your viewing experience with high-quality streaming on any device.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="description">
    <h2 data-aos="fade-zoom-in" data-aos-duration="1000" data-aos-offset="250" class="text-end">User's Content</h2>
    <p data-aos="fade-right" data-aos-duration="1000" data-aos-delay="100" data-aos-offset="250">
      Welcome to the heart of our community! Immerse yourself in a world of laughter, creativity,
      and positivity. Explore an endless array of hilarious memes and positive vibes, where
      laughter knows no bounds. Join our vibrant community and unleash the joy of sharing and
      creating memes together. Connect with like-minded individuals, browse through an abundance of
      memes, and create your own to share with the world.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="image-container">
    <img
      src="img/drakeExplains.jpg"
      alt=""
      data-aos="fade-up"
      data-aos-duration="1000"
      data-aos-offset="250"
    />
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <a href="/register" class="btn btn-dark btn-lg mt-4" style="font-size: 24px; padding: 15px 30px" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1000" data-aos-delay="200">Register</a>
</section>

<footer class="py-5 bg-dark">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="m-0 text-center text-white">Copyright &copy; FlickFusion 2023</p>
  </div>
</footer>

<script src="https://unpkg.com/aos@next/dist/aos.js"></script>
<script>
  AOS.init();
</script>
</body>

</html>
